  <dmn:decision id="_04ceea5e-e4ab-4ec8-8a53-91ad256143d3" name="FlightDetails">
    <dmn:description>## What it decides
Use this decision to classify the flight&apos;s inherent DVT risk based on distance and duration.
## Call when
- Evaluating how the flight profile contributes to overall DVT risk.
## Do not call when
- Flight data is unavailable or the trip is non-air travel.
## Inputs
- FlightData.Distance (number, &lt;30000 km) — total flight distance.
- FlightData.Duration (number, 0–48 hrs) — total flight duration.
## Output
- `&quot;Low&quot;`: short-haul (&lt;5000 km) and short duration (&lt;8 hrs).
- `&quot;Moderate&quot;`: either long distance or long duration, but not both.
- `&quot;High&quot;`: long-haul (≥5000 km) AND long duration (≥8 hrs).
## Examples
- 3000 km, 4 hrs → `&quot;Low&quot;`
- 7000 km, 10 hrs → `&quot;High&quot;`</dmn:description>
    <dmn:extensionElements />
