  <dmn:decision id="_e6084413-3bf9-4e06-a2ba-6e2448289922" name="FlightRiskDVT">
    <dmn:description>## What it decides
Use this decision to combine flight profile, patient DVT risk factors, and CHF risk into an overall DVT risk rating.
## Call when
- All three sub-assessments (FlightDetails, DVTRiskFactors, CHFRisk) are available.
## Do not call when
- Any upstream decision has not been evaluated.
## Inputs
- FlightDetails (tFlightDetails) — flight-based risk level.
- DVTRiskFactors (tFlightDetails) — patient-based risk level.
- CHFRisk (tFlightDetails) — cardiac-based risk level.
## Output
- `&quot;High&quot;`: any single High, or two Moderates.
- `&quot;Moderate&quot;`: exactly one Moderate with the others Low.
- `&quot;Low&quot;`: all three are Low.
## Examples
- High, Low, Low → `&quot;High&quot;`
- Moderate, Moderate, Low → `&quot;High&quot;`
- Low, Moderate, Low → `&quot;Moderate&quot;`
- Low, Low, Low → `&quot;Low&quot;`</dmn:description>
    <dmn:extensionElements />
    <dmn:variable id="_c34931a5-03b0-4e94-8286-b7b92269316d" name="FlightRiskDVT" typeRef="tFlightDetails" />
